WILLTORUN leaned out and bumped a rival at the start, stalked along the inside, took aim off of the fence nearing the lane, but lacked a bid, sparred with an outer rival for place and prevailed. AXTHELM took contact from an outer rival at the start, pressed two wide and between horses, got floated to the four path by an inner foe nearing the lane, dueled with that one for place through midstretch but yielded late. B D VALESKI bumped with an inner rival at the start, settled off of the pace in the three path, fanned six wide entering the lane and rallied. GREGORY'S PRIDE laid off of the pace along the inside, then stayed on in the two path and between horses but failed to menace. LEGAL ATTACK (GB) broke a step slow while taking contact from an inner rival at the start, tracked two wide and between horses but gave way. ZATIP tracked three wide and between horses and faded. FAUCI trailed two wide, shifted out in midstretch and made little impact. SAMBURU (GB) stalked three wide, but gave way in the five path turning for home and weakened between horses. OF THE MOMENT bounced off an outer rival into an inner foe at the start, pursued from midpack four wide, fanned seven wide into the lane and tired.
